                <formulaTemplate>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To cancel an open order using the Ndax mobile app, follow these steps:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
1. Log in to the Ndax mobile app.&lt;br&gt;
2. Tap the Markets icon on the bottom left.&lt;br&gt;
3. It looks like a bar or graph.&lt;br&gt;
4. Select the cryptocurrency you want to cancel the open order for.&lt;br&gt;
5. Tap the Orders tab at the bottom left of the screen.&lt;br&gt;
6. Scroll through your list of open orders and tap the three dots next to the order you want to cancel.&lt;br&gt;
7. Tap the trash can labelled Cancel Order.&lt;br&gt;
8. On the confirmation screen, tap Yes, Cancel Order to complete the cancellation.&lt;/p&gt;</formulaTemplate>
